      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "STARTYOURENGINE (4) has been knocking on the door this prep and continued the trend with a solid third over 1400m at this track last time out. He strips fitter and from a favourable draw, he gets every chance to break through. RIVERINA WALTZ (5) relocated from NSW, and she is better than her last start suggests when fifth at Wagga over 1300m  just over 5 weeks ago, and she is capable of improving sharply at her first local start. IZ SHAFT (3) has raced his way into form, placing over this course at his latest outing here just over 6 weeks ago, and he should take further improvement from that performance. He shapes as a genuine each-way contender. DENUTO (1) has been thereabouts this prep and is well drawn. Stick with him on an each-way basis. FLAVIUS (2) will start from the pole position and he has some rough claims in a modest field.",
